original_title: The Haunted Baby Carriage From Hell
overview: In this LGBTQ+ Horror Comedy Short Film, Spencer and Cameron move into a new house that just so happens to be haunted by an old baby carriage. As the carriage endeavors to scare the couple, the attempts ultimately fail because the couple just doesn't care... like... you know... at all.
tagline: Some baby carriages aren't for babies
title: The Haunted Baby Carriage From Hell
